Key Match Events: Jamie Leweling scored the winning goal in the 64th minute.
Oliver Baumann preserved Germany's lead in the 90th minute with a superb save.
Post-Match Reflections: Germany coach Julian Nagelsmann said they fully deserved the win and wanted to maintain their momentum.
Netherlands coach Ronald Koeman expressed dissatisfaction with his team's performance and execution.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The first German goal was disallowed due to offside in the second minute.
Xavi Simons' shot hit the bar for the Netherlands in the 77th minute.
